  "response": "As an AI, I don't have personal opinions, but I can share that the best Batman actor often sparks lively debate among fans. Each actor has brought something unique to the role:\n\n- **Adam West** is beloved for his campy and humorous portrayal in the 1960s TV show.\n- **Michael Keaton** is often praised for his darker, more complex take in Tim Burton's films.\n- **Christian Bale** received acclaim for his intense and gritty interpretation in Christopher Nolan's trilogy.\n- **Ben Affleck** brought a different, more experienced version of Bruce Wayne in the DCEU films.\n- **Robert Pattinson** has also received positive feedback for his portrayal in \"The Batman,\" emphasizing a more detective-oriented approach.\n\nUltimately, opinions on the best Batman often depend on individual preferences regarding tone, style, and interpretation of the character.",
